Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:03.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The hero, Sink, suddenly appeared in Biscotti.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.69,0:00:06.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, he's unable to return to his homeworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.35,0:00:08.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it has nothing to do with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.82,0:00:12.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So we, Genoise, have kidnapped the princess without giving a damn about the situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.77,0:00:15.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and we even declared war!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.13,0:00:18.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, it's time I show up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.30,0:00:19.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Gaul! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:10.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Though the heat from the afternoon war hasn't yet settled,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.96,0:02:13.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it seems like something big has happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.61,0:02:22.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The representative of Biscotti, \NPrincess Millhiore, has been abducted!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.57,0:02:25.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Franboise, as your temporary live host,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.85,0:02:29.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,am heading to the battleground as fast as I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.39,0:02:33.34,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(500,0)\pos(343,359)}  「Charge! The War to Recover the Princess!! 」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.48,0:02:37.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.53,0:02:39.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:42.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad. The princess was kidnapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:44.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I need to rescue her right away{\fscx230}-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.15,0:02:47.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You... idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.12,0:02:55.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt! What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.93,0:02:59.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's supposed to be my line, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:01.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The heck are you doing? How can you accept the declaration just like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.03,0:03:04.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.27,0:03:09.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Amelita.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.01,0:03:13.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't tell the hero about the rules \Nregarding the notice for a declaration of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.47,0:03:14.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:18.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.93,0:03:21.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll bring the princess back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.40,0:03:25.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But will we make it in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.96,0:03:32.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't disappoint the people who were\Nlooking forward to hearing the princess sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:34.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.42,0:03:37.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Hero and Eclair have already taken off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:40.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll gather the soldiers and move out right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:45.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're... Homura?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.67,0:03:51.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you accept the notice for a declaration of war,\Nit'll become an official acknowledgment of war!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.85,0:03:53.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay to battle during normal times,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.89,0:03:57.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but why choose the time when the princess is about to hold a celebratory dinner party?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.47,0:04:02.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are only one and a half hours before the princess's show begins!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:04.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening, Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:06.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm listening. I-I really am!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:10.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And why can't you even ride a cerkle properly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:11.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:15.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair, if you get too angry, your blood vessels might burst.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:23.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair, Ricotta, I'm sorry for acting on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.07,0:04:31.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In my world, it's serious when bad guys kidnap a princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.98,0:04:35.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why there's no way I can keep silent!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:38.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it'll be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:40.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save the princess,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:43.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll make sure she's on time for her concert!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.29,0:04:46.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:49.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm weak, I'll try my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:53.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Thanks, Ricotta, Eclair!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.79,0:05:04.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:07.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find something interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:11.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yukikaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.94,0:05:15.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like there's gonna be a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.17,0:05:34.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, it is a great honor to be called forth by you, Prince Gaul.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.13,0:05:40.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, judging from your looks, I'm sure you haven't had your share of fun today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:42.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can bet on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:48.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Although the fortress attack was not bad, \Nmy expertise tends to lie with night battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:51.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! Go as crazy as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:54.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, have a drink! Eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:57.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. I'll take you up on your offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.14,0:06:08.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by the way, where is Princess Millhiore right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:11.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rouge is taking care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.94,0:06:13.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm giving her first-class treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.95,0:06:15.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.84,0:06:21.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After that... I happen to have a little idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:36.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.94,0:06:41.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Princess Mi, sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.47,0:06:44.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've brought Bano and her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.75,0:06:48.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Rouge!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.56,0:06:52.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long, Bano.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:54.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to see that you're healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:03.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The kids look great too! What a healthy bunch! {she said "this year's kids".. probably this animal gives birth every year... lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:11.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Gaul says that Bano would want to show you how well her kids are doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.46,0:07:14.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Gaul is so thoughtful as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:16.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:17.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:24.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like the war hasn't started.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:28.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are willing, please talk with Prince Gaul for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:31.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get him to come over right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:34.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Please do so, Rouge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.41,0:07:54.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bano, is your mistress,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.56,0:07:57.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Leo, doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:08:02.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We used to travel to each other's countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.13,0:08:05.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our friendship was supposed to be wonderful,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.64,0:08:12.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but these days she rarely meets with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:16.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The only topic of conversation that we have is related to war.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:23.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you tell her, on my behalf, that I am very lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.23,0:08:38.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to wait for the main force, but we've run out of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:42.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Gaul's men are all elites.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:46.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be very difficult to fight so many enemies in the wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.05,0:08:50.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, back in previous wars,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:54.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there was one who faced armies of over a thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.95,0:09:12.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was a legendary knight who forced \Nher way through a whole army by herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:13.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:17.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to that, we're about to \Nface only a mere hundred enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:20.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. We've got Rico's support too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:23.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.54,0:09:25.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And we won't make it if we don't strike now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:28.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take the shortest route with the fastest speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.53,0:09:31.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Front breakthrough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:37.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The ear drooping captain and the hero are really coming head on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:41.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well! We'll send them back where they came from!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:44.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Archers, be ready with your bows!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.61,0:10:00.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're under attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:05.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're using artillery?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:12.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:17.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the Chief Science Researcher of Biscotti, Ricotta Elmar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:35.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And on the battlefield, I use artillery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.65,0:10:51.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:56.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Although it's tough to differentiate who is who in this darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.27,0:10:59.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see that the young knights are fighting hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.94,0:11:02.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, my Lady,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:05.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,this seems to be a war between Biscotti and Galette.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:08.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't we lend a helping hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.53,0:11:13.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's just joyful combat between the youngsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:16.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't be nice if adults joined in and spoiled the fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:21.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just kick back and enjoy the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:32.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Homura. Please deliver this letter to your mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:34.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very urgent!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.65,0:11:52.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a grand welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.09,0:11:54.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what I like!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:12:00.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.39,0:12:01.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:33.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:35.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Gaul!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.78,0:12:39.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.96,0:12:44.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for the sudden abduction,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:47.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I just happen to have my own plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:49.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:53.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but do allow me to challenge your hero to a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:55.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll discuss compensation and \Nother troublesome matters later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:01.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:04.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get going then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.08,0:13:24.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the Captain of the \NImperial Guard and the hero are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.06,0:13:28.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rico's bombardment has stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.22,0:13:29.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.55,0:13:33.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.56,0:13:36.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Once an artillery user runs into infantry, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:39.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, I'd want to compliment her for lasting this long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.80,0:13:44.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My master, Prince Gaul, has asked to see this so-called Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:46.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow us to the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.79,0:13:53.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no longer any of your business, young captain girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.99,0:13:57.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you surrender now, I will let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.38,0:13:58.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:02.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Then,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.91,0:14:07.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just make you suffer for a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.60,0:14:09.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.60,0:14:09.64,Dialogue Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.59,0:14:12.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:13.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:15.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, listen up...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:16.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Eclair, you listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:19.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay here! You go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:19.46,Dialogue Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay here! You go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:23.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you imitate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:26.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line, you perverted hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.39,0:14:29.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, just go! It's dangerous here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.57,0:14:32.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're more familiar with the inside of the fortress, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.09,0:14:36.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you able to tackle something difficult like deterring enemies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:38.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you should just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.18,0:14:41.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As if I could let a girl face danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:43.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever! I'm asking you to go, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:45.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave this place to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:46.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough! Just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:48.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so stubborn?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.27,0:14:54.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you kids! Stop fooling around at a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.49,0:15:10.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're up against me and a hundred \Nsoldiers from the Galette Lion Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.23,0:15:15.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe they sent a childish hero and a low class practicing knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:19.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can retaliate,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:25.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,show me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:46.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This sword is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.56,0:15:48.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.46,0:15:54.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time, Eclair!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:57.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen you for a while, and you've grown so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:16:00.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady d'Arquien!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:03.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,d'Arquien, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:04.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.14,0:16:10.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Axe General and Sir Hero, this should be the first time we have met.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:13.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a freelance knight among the Knights of Biscotti,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.76,0:16:15.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the Leader of the Onmitsu Squad,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.71,0:16:17.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Brioche d'Arquien!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.86,0:16:24.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In response to a plea from the Leader of the Knights, Laurent, I'm here to assist in this battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:29.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out! Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.21,0:16:32.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Crest Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.38,0:16:36.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gale Beeline!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:56.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the help, Sir Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:16:58.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:02.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right, I was still in the middle of introducing myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:04.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, where was I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:10.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well. So I'm here to participate in the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.26,0:17:12.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:18.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.53,0:17:21.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.94,0:17:24.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose idea was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:33.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am from the Onmitsu Squad of Biscotti's Knight Army...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.18,0:17:35.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! When did she...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.08,0:17:38.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you'd let me finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.52,0:17:40.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Crest Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.05,0:17:46.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukikaze Style Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:47.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Old style,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:49.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Locus...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.00,0:17:58.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:08.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,From the Onmitsu Squad of Biscotti's Knight Army,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:11.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Yukikaze Panettone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.97,0:18:18.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki, we've got the fireworks and the explosives!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.69,0:18:20.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice job, Rico!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.36,0:18:28.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, all the soldiers who captured you are now sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.68,0:18:31.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll need someone to collect them later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.97,0:18:37.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Rico, let's go assist the Lady and Eclair and the other guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.41,0:18:39.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.78,0:18:54.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! They're at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.47,0:18:57.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go out with a big bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.69,0:18:58.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!{Gozaru!}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.43,0:19:05.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rico and Yuki Style Bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:09.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One Hundred Flower Types!{Hundred Variety Flowers!}{lit. Profusion Large Varieties of Flowers}{AL: appreciate it if anyone can come up with a cooler name}{yeah... any other suggestions are good...}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:27.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair, I think... I think something happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:29.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:33.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady d'Arquien, I'm Eclair Martinozzi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:40.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We've decided to break inside and save the princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:43.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:45.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukikaze and I will take care of things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:02.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:06.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gaul, that idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.84,0:20:09.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He kidnapped her without my consent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:12.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rouge should be there watching over him,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:15.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but it must have been his stubbornness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.59,0:20:17.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.38,0:20:22.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How can we allow a country and a feudal lord's command to be harassed by childish games?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.38,0:20:30.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you must be the Hero of Biscotti?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.80,0:20:33.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Galette's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.61,0:20:39.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you don't want to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.83,0:20:48.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I'll listen to your introduction later!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:50.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm taking the princess back with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.17,0:20:55.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem, if you can do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:04.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the three fools have finally appeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.12,0:21:05.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling a fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.96,0:21:07.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The one calling another a fool is a fool herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.72,0:21:09.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Fool! Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.71,0:21:14.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you three are my \Nopponents gives me a big headache.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.07,0:21:17.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As one of the Imperial Guards myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.10,0:21:21.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,allow me, Noir Vinocacao, to take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.12,0:21:23.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And me, Vert Farble!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.77,0:21:26.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair, I challenge you to a fair fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:29.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just that it's three against one!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.75,0:21:32.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Jaune Clafoutis, will do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.16,0:21:35.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the Captain of the Imperial \NGuard from Biscotti's Knight Army,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.01,0:21:37.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair Martinozzi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.23,0:21:39.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will break my way through and proceed forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:49.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad for a knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.56,0:21:54.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.86,0:21:57.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.72,0:22:00.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Very soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.83,0:22:04.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,ED
